window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Fall in love at Bayside, where sandy beaches, good friends, and true love come together in the sweet small towns of Cape Cod. </p> <p>Bayside Summers is a series of standalone steamy romance novels featuring alpha male heroes and sexy, empowered women. They're fun, flirty, flawed, deeply emotional, always passionate, and easy to relate to. Bayside Summers is part of the Love in Bloom romance collection by <i>New York Times</i> and <i>USA Today</i> best-selling and award-winning author Melissa Foster. While each audiobook may be listened to as a standalone, you might enjoy listening to the entire Love in Bloom series. Characters from each sub-series appear in future audiobooks. </p> <p>In <i>Bayside Desires</i>... </p> <p>As the co-owner of Bayside Resorts, Rick Savage has a fabulous beachfront resort where he works with his best friends and brother, and plenty of beautiful women to keep him company. When Desiree Cleary moves in next door to take care of her mother's estate, Rick sets his sights on the sexy and oh-so sweet pre-school teacher. But Desiree's sister isn't keen on the fast-talking playboy making moves on the younger sister she's never had a chance to get to know. And she has other ideas in store - like opening Summers Inn, a bed and breakfast that could be big-time competition for Rick's resort. </p> <p>All Bayside books can be listened to as standalone audiobooks or as part of the series: </p> <p>Coming Soon... </p> <p></p> <ul> <li><i>Bayside Heat</i> </li> <li><i>Bayside Escape </i></li> <li><i>Bayside Fantasies</i> </li> <li><i>Bayside Romance</i> </li> <li><i>Bayside Passions</i> </li> </ul> <p></p> <p><i>Bayside Summers</i> is part of the Love in Bloom romance collection. Characters from each sub-series appear in future audiobooks. Visit Melissa's website for Love in Bloom family trees, series checklists, and more. </p>"; 
